113
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:40,160
Huh?

114
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,200
Oh.

115
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:55,880
Hey.

116
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,360
How are you?

117
