126
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:49,600
Hey, I want to get ice cream from this shop.

127
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,160
Okay.

128
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:53,080
Hey, P' Yu, wait a second, come here.

129
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:54,560
What's up?

130
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:58,120
I forgot my wallet,

131
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,240
