133
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,360
Why don’t you borrow from me first?

134
00:09:03,880 --> 00:09:05,880
Come on, we’re all buying together.

135
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,400
One chocolate,

136
00:09:08,400 --> 00:09:10,760
