137
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,120
You eat a lot.

138
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:17,560
I bought them for you guys, one each.

139
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:22,960
Want anything else?

140
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,400
Hey, where's P' Yu going?

141
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,720
Follow me when you're done.

142
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,720
Wait, P' Yu!

143
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,560
Hey, wait.

144
00:09:31,280 --> 00:09:33,280
You haven't even gotten your ice cream yet, where are you going?

145
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:38,120
You invited me to eat, so you have to wait.

146
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:48,520
Ai, you seem to really like sweets.

147
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,480
Everything looks so good, doesn't it?

148
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:54,120
But I can't decide what to choose.

149
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:57,160
Have you tried this one before?

150
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,720
Hmm... no, I haven't.

151
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,320
I will buy it for you.

152
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:09,320
Hello, one portion of sesame rice dessert, please.

153
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,600
Thank you.

154
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:17,680
Wow, bought so many things.

155
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,680
Alright, let me feed you.

156
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:43,560
Hmm, it's delicious.

157
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,400
That's great, P'Waan.

158
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:50,000
