159
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:52,120
No idea, but it's really good.

160
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,440
This is called sesame rice dessert.

161
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:56,280
It's made from sticky rice that's steamed,

162
00:10:56,280 --> 00:11:00,240
and then pounded together with sesame seeds, like those over there.

163
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:01,080
Hmm.

164
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,800
Shall we go have a look over there?

165
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:05,480
Sure.

166
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,920
Want me to carry this for you?

167
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:08,320
Come on.
No, it's okay.

168
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:14,720
Can I get a slice of pizza?

169
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:15,520
Sure.

170
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:16,760
Thank you.

171
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,280
It's all over your mouth.

172
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:38,960
Thank you.

173
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:46,280
Hey, do you guys want to something fun?

174
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:46,960
Sure.

175
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:52,200
Uh, truth or dare?

176
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:52,880
Hmm.

177
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:55,200
Alright, if you ask and can't answer, you have to take a shot.

178
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:58,880
But if you dare and don't do it, you have to finish your drink.

179
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,560
Sounds fun, let's do it.

180
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:04,040
Who said I was going to play?

181
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:07,480
Come on, we don't get together like this often.

182
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:10,080
If you get drunk, we'll take care of you.

183
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,120
Hurry up, let's go.

184
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:13,720
Come on.

185
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:15,480
Okay, here we go.

186
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:17,800
Whoever the arrow points to first, they're up.

187
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:18,400
Umm.

188
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:18,880
Let's go.

189
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:21,680
Who?

190
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:23,000
There it is.

191
00:12:28,400 --> 00:12:29,400
(Ai.)

192
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:32,200
