241
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:17,640
Give a kiss on the head to the person across from you.

242
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:19,640
Hey, Ai!

243
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:20,680
Let's do it.

244
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:21,280
What?

245
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:23,080
Come on, hurry up, stop stalling.

246
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,760
Hurry up.
No.

247
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,200
Hurry, it's just a game.

248
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,000
Hurry up, Ing.

249
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,760
You guys wanted to play this yourselves.

250
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:30,080
I don't want to do.

251
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:34,840
Ing, Yo! Ing, Yo! Ing, Yo!

252
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,280
Hurry up.

253
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:36,840
Come on.

254
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:38,600
Yay, that's it.

255
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,360
