260
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,400
Shall we continue the game?

261
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:49,080
Come on.

262
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:49,600
Ai.

263
00:14:54,400 --> 00:14:55,360
(Ai)

264
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,440
