268
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:06,640
(P' Waan)

269
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:10,000
Go ahead and ask, P' Waan.

270
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,080
I can...

271
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:12,760
