282
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,680
If you don’t answer, you have to drink.

283
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:47,080
Oh.

284
00:15:53,760 --> 00:15:54,280
Alright.

285
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:55,800
That’s it then.

286
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:58,600
What’s going on? Everyone’s waiting for your answer.

287
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,680
Shall we start a new round?

288
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,240
Next round, everyone.

289
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:06,680
(P'  Yu.)

290
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:09,680
It's P'  Yu's turn!

291
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,640
True or dare?

292
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:12,800
Dare.

293
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,080
He's brave!

294
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:14,600
Come on.

295
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:16,360
(Ing)

296
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:17,640
P' Yu.

297
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:18,560
Calm down, Ing.

298
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:20,400
I’m sorry.

299
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:21,360
Come on.

300
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:25,040
Stare at the person opposite you for one minute.

301
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,320
Up close.

302
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:27,600
And why me?

303
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,480
Well, you played me last round.

304
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:31,400
So I’m getting my revenge.

305
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,840
Are you scared?

306
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:36,680
Why would I be scared? Of course I’m not.

307
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:37,800
Let's start.

308
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:40,440
Yo, start the timer.

309
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,880
One minute, everyone.

310
00:16:43,040 --> 00:16:46,640
One, two, three.

311
00:16:59,640 --> 00:17:01,400
A little closer

312
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:02,760
Go, Ai, hold your ground.

313
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:04,280
A bit closer.

314
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:06,120
Alright.

315
00:17:17,280 --> 00:17:18,960
But it hasn’t even been a minute yet.

316
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:19,960
Huh, not yet?

317
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,560
Uh, it’s only been forty seconds.

318
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,240
I think that’s enough.

319
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:25,400
Consider it a tie.

320
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,760
Both are losers.

321
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,920
Both of you drink a full glass.

322
00:17:31,840 --> 00:17:34,600
It’s okay, I’ll drink it for him.

323
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:35,720
Is that alright, Yo?

324
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,040
Sure.

325
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,480
Do I have to drink mine too?

326
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:49,240
Well, you're drinking Ai’s and you haven't started yours yet.

327
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:50,000
Got it.

328
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,800
Keep it up, P'  Yu.

329
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:01,000
How about a final toast?

330
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,160
More?

331
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:02,680
Just a bit.

332
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,560
Just a little, for tradition.

333
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:04,040
Just a little bit.

334
00:18:04,040 --> 00:18:05,120
Okay.

335
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:06,120
Let’s clink glasses.

336
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:07,320
Oh, cheers!

337
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:11,400
Let’s clink glasses.

338
00:18:14,520 --> 00:18:16,520
You guys just keep cheering non-stop.

339
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:24,680
I’ll need to the bathroom first.

340
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:26,200
Go ahead.

341
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:28,920
Are you alright?

342
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:30,280
I'm ok.

343
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:31,720
Yo, your friend.

344
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:35,640
He's so drunk that he's not walking straight.

345
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:38,120
Why did you guys stop drinking?

346
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:40,120
Come on, cheers.

347
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:43,080
Hey.

348
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:45,480
Hey, are you ok?

349
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:49,800
Get up, come on.

350
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:55,360
I think I should take Ai to bed.

351
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:56,800
Do you need my help?

352
00:18:58,400 --> 00:18:58,920
It's ok.

353
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:00,400
Stay with your friend.

354
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:01,520
Sure.

355
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,440
You rarely get to hang out like this.

356
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:04,920
Take care.

357
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:09,280
That's enough, you still want more?

358
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:09,880
Let's get you to bed.

359
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:11,440
Yo.

360
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:12,040
That's enough.

361
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:32,600
Are P'  Yu and Ai really that close?

362
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:37,000
Well, they grew up together,

363
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,880
so it's only natural they're close.

364
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:43,520
But what about you? You've been with Ai all day today.

365
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,800
Do you like Ai that much?

366
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:52,240
I’ve been meaning to ask you this a few times already.

367
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,800
Can you tell me...

368
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:56,480
why you like Ai so much?

369
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:57,440
Could you tell me?

370
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:02,800
Do you remember...

371
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:06,760
the time I lost during the university tryouts?

372
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,280
This is for you.

373
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:30,400
For me?

374
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:41,240
I’ve been cheering you on. You're amazing, keep it up!

375
00:20:44,360 --> 00:20:45,520
Thank you so much.

376
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:47,520
Yeah.

377
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:02,960
Why are you smiling like that?

378
00:21:03,600 --> 00:21:05,800
What’s on your mind? Can you tell me?

379
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,160
Oh, it’s nothing.

380
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:10,440
I just like him.

381
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:15,640
Okay, let me help you out then.

382
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:17,720
How could you possibly help me?

383
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:21,360
I can help you with anything you need.

384
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:32,720
Where did P' Yu and Ai go?

385
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,080
P' Yu took Ai to bed.

386
00:21:35,800 --> 00:21:36,920
But tonight, you’re sleeping with me.

387
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:39,520
Let Ai sleep with P' Yu.

388
00:21:41,320 --> 00:21:42,120
Then...

389
00:21:43,080 --> 00:21:44,880
you two go ahead and continue drinking.

390
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:47,240
I'm going to head home.

391
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:54,160
Everybody is leaving me.

392
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:55,720
Hey, wait.

393
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:57,840
Where are you going?

394
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:00,000
I'm going to go to bed.

395
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:01,200
No.

396
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,240
You have to stay and play with me first.

397
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:06,040
What do I get from playing with you?

398
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:07,680
You get to play.

399
00:22:08,360 --> 00:22:11,000
Or you can just give up like the rest of them, I'm fine with that.

400
00:22:11,760 --> 00:22:12,760
Come on.

401
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:13,480
You wanna have go?

402
00:22:14,120 --> 00:22:16,240
Just don't throw up.

403
00:22:16,480 --> 00:22:18,840
I’m a gold standard drinker, you know!

404
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:21,120
Whoever finishes first wins!

405
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:23,000
Alright, let's go!

406
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:31,920
Yes! I won!

407
00:22:32,560 --> 00:22:34,360
Do you want to head back and sleep first?

408
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:37,080
You alright, Yo?

409
00:22:38,280 --> 00:22:40,000
I told you to drink less.

410
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:45,840
I’ll go get you a change of clothes, hang tight.

411
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:49,640
Hey, Ing, come here for a sec.

412
00:22:52,360 --> 00:22:53,560
You know what?

413
00:22:53,920 --> 00:22:56,520
You’re the best friend I’ve ever had in this world.

414
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:00,880
We’re such good friends, huh?

415
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,040
Do friends...

416
00:23:07,120 --> 00:23:08,400
usually do like this?

417
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:12,240
Well,

418
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:14,920
we’re friends, right?

419
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:17,360
But... don't you love me the way...

420
00:23:18,120 --> 00:23:19,040
I love you?

421
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,440
I love you,

422
00:23:41,040 --> 00:23:42,760
but not as a friend.

423
00:23:55,920 --> 00:23:57,200
I know.

424
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:03,320
I love you just like...

425
00:24:06,080 --> 00:24:06,800
Yo...

426
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:11,760
Are you okay?

427
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:21,720
Argh, Yo.

428
00:24:23,280 --> 00:24:24,200
Just a sec, we're almost there.

429
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:52,960
Ai, come on.

430
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,200
Ooh, P' Yu.

431
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:56,960
Wait for me.

432
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:57,680
Quickly.

433
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,200
Wait for me.

434
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:00,640
Shit!!

435
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:04,360
P' Yu!

436
00:26:23,880 --> 00:26:24,920
P' Yu, what are you doing here?

437
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,440
Where's Ing?

438
00:26:30,360 --> 00:26:32,160
I think he's sleeping in Yo's room.

439
00:26:37,800 --> 00:26:40,240
Don't tell me you don’t remember anything.

440
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:43,200
Remember what?

441
00:26:47,600 --> 00:26:48,560
Everything?

442
00:26:50,080 --> 00:26:50,760
Why?

443
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:52,840
What did I do?
